N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4003.2 - Enfranchised associations

State Regulations

All provisions in this Subchapter affecting licensed
racing associations shall be applicable also to franchised racing associations, racing corporations, and franchised racing corporations except as may be
otherwise provided by law. Notes
